032/**
033 * An immutable {@link List} of {@link TypeMirror}s sorted in a specific way, intended to store the {@linkplain
034 * Types#supertypes(TypeMirror) supertypes} of a {@link TypeMirror}.
035 *
036 * @author <a href="https://about.me/lairdnelson" target="_top">Laird Nelson</a>
037 *
038 * @see Types#supertypes(TypeMirror)
039 */
040public final class SupertypeList implements List<TypeMirror> {
041
042  private static final SupertypeList EMPTY_LIST = new SupertypeList();
043
044  private final int interfaceIndex;
045
046  private final List<TypeMirror> sortedSupertypes;
047
048  private SupertypeList() {
049    this(List.of(), -1);
050  }
051
052  SupertypeList(final List<? extends TypeMirror> sortedSupertypes, final int interfaceIndex) {
053    super();
054    if (sortedSupertypes.isEmpty()) {
055      if (interfaceIndex >= 0) {
056        throw new IllegalArgumentException("sortedSupertypes: " + sortedSupertypes + "; interfaceIndex: " + interfaceIndex);
057      }
058      this.sortedSupertypes = List.of();
059      this.interfaceIndex = interfaceIndex;
060    } else {
061      switch (sortedSupertypes) {
062      case SupertypeList sl:
063        this.sortedSupertypes = sl.sortedSupertypes;
064        this.interfaceIndex = sl.interfaceIndex;
065        break;
066      default:
067        this.sortedSupertypes = List.copyOf(sortedSupertypes);
068        this.interfaceIndex = interfaceIndex;
069      }
070    }
071  }
072
